Package controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminController
    Controller class for admin view, where the admin can create/delete users.
    InsideAlbumController
    Controller class for album view where a user can add/delete photos from an album, copy/move photos between albums, start a slideshow to view photos, or view a single photos.
    LoginController
    Controller for the login view of the application.
    PhotoDisplayController
    Controller class for photo view, where a single photo is displayed along with its relevant information.
    SearchController
    Controller class for search view where a user can search for photos in all their albums by either date or by tag.
    SlideShowController
    Controller for slideshow view where photos can be viewed in sequence.
    UserAlbumController
    Controller class for user view, where a user can view a list of existing albums, create/delete albums, or go to the search view to search for photos, or go to album view to manage an album.
